"title": "1045: God, glory of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1045",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The revelation of God's power and characteristics, sometimes accompanied by visible phenomena.</p>\n<h2>Glory as an attribute of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:7-Ps24:8\">PSA 24:7–24:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3\">PSA 29:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:40\">JHN 11:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:2\">ACT 7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:1\">REV 19:1</a></p>\n<h2>Visible phenomena accompanying God's glory</h2>\n<h3>The appearance of God's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:4\">HAB 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:24\">DEU 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:8-2Sam22:16\">2SA 22:8–22:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:7-Ps18:15\">PSA 18:7–18:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1\">PSA 104:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:26-Ezek1:28\">EZK 1:26–1:28</a></p>\n<h3>God's glory as a cloud</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:15-Exod24:16\">EXO 24:15–24:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:9-Exod33:10\">EXO 33:9–33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:5\">ISA 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:34\">LUK 9:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">LUK 21:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">MAT 24:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">MRK 13:26</a></p>\n<h3>God's glory in the tabernacle and the temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13-2Chr5:14\">2CH 5:13–5:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1KI 8:10–8:11</a> <em>The Jewish term for the outward sign of God's presence in the temple is “Shekinah”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:35\">EXO 40:34–40:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:1-2Chr7:3\">2CH 7:1–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:4\">EZK 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:19\">EZK 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:1-Ezek43:5\">EZK 43:1–43:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:8\">REV 15:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory revealed</h2>\n<h3>In Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:3\">ISA 49:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:31-John13:32\">JHN 13:31–13:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:5\">JHN 17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>In his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:19-Isa60:21\">ISA 60:19–60:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:3\">ISA 62:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:21\">EPH 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>In the whole world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">ISA 6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:21\">NUM 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:5\">PSA 57:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:11\">PSA 57:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:5\">PSA 108:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:14\">HAB 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:3\">HAB 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>In heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:23\">REV 21:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9\">HEB 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>In his name</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:5\">NEH 9:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:58\">DEU 28:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:13\">1CH 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:1\">PSA 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:9\">PSA 79:9</a></p>\n<h3>In his works</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:3\">PSA 111:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1\">PSA 19:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:5\">ISA 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:2\">ISA 35:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:40-John11:44\">JHN 11:40–11:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a></p>\n<h3>In his kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:11-Ps145:12\">PSA 145:11–145:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11\">1CH 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory cannot be fully seen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15-1Tim6:16\">1TI 6:15–6:16</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:18-Exod33:20\">EXO 33:18–33:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:22-Judg6:23\">JDG 6:22–6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:20-Judg13:22\">JDG 13:20–13:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a></p>\n<h2>God's glory experienced</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55\">ACT 7:55</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:2\">EXO 3:2</a> <em>Moses</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1-Isa6:4\">ISA 6:1–6:4</a> <em>Isaiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:9\">LUK 2:9</a> <em>the shepherds</em></p>\n<h2>The effects of God's glory</h2>\n<h3>God's glory is acknowledged</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:19\">PSA 72:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:2\">PSA 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:36\">ROM 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:13\">REV 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:1\">REV 19:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's glory brings guilt and fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:10\">ISA 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:19\">ISA 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:21\">ISA 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:13\">REV 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:8\">REV 15:8</a></p>",
